title: Ravens' Zay Flowers (calf) DNP again on Thursday
text: Ravens' Zay Flowers (calf) DNP again on Thursday Baltimore Ravens wide receiver Zay Flowers (calf) did not practice on Thursday ahead of Week 17's game against the Miami Dolphins. Flowers continues to deal with a calf injury and missed his second practice of the week on Thursday. Two missed practices to start the week have Flowers uncertain to play against the Dolphins. Friday's practice report will provide more information. Flowers' Week 17 projection includes 4.9 receptions, 56.3 yards, 0.38 touchdowns, and 11.2 FanDuel points.
